duties_responsibilities.duty: Perform fast-paced and physical warehouse duties including loading, unloading, and sorting of packages of various sizes.
Work one shift a day for part-time employees and two shifts for full-time employees, with variable shift lengths based on package volume.
Adhere to safety protocols and procedures to ensure workplace safety and prevent accidents.
Collaborate with team members to efficiently and effectively complete tasks and meet productivity targets.
Report and address any issues or discrepancies with packages and shipments.
